---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Shivchay Moharan - Praises of Rebbe Nachman" description="Testimonials and praises about Rebbe Nachman of Breslov from his students and followers">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>Shivchay Moharan</h1>
    <p>שיבחו מוהרן</p>
    <a href="/teachings" class="back-link">← Back to Teachings</a>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="description">
        <strong>Shivchay Moharan</strong> (Praises of Our Teacher Rabbi Nachman) is a collection 
        of testimonials, praises, and accounts from students and followers who witnessed 
        Rebbe Nachman's greatness firsthand. This work contains stories of miraculous events, 
        accounts of his extraordinary wisdom, and heartfelt expressions of gratitude for his 
        guidance and influence on countless lives.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="topics">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Contents</h2>
      <div class="topics-grid">
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Testimonials from Students</h3>
          <p>First-hand accounts from those who learned directly from Rebbe Nachman</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Miraculous Events</h3>
          <p>Stories of supernatural occurrences and divine intervention</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Healing Accounts</h3>
          <p>Testimonies of physical and spiritual healings</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Wisdom & Insight</h3>
          <p>Examples of Rebbe Nachman's extraordinary wisdom and knowledge</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Love & Connection</h3>
          <p>Stories of Rebbe Nachman's boundless love for his followers</p>
        </div>
        <div class="topic-card">
          <h3>Final Days</h3>
          <p>Accounts of Rebbe Nachman's last days and passing</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quote">
    <div class="container">
      <blockquote>
        <p class="hebrew">כי אין בעולם כמוהו צדיק גדול כמוהו</p>
        <p>"For there is no tzadik in the world like him."</p>
        <cite>— A student's testimony</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="featured-praises">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Featured Testimonials</h2>
      <div class="praise-list">
        <div class="praise-item">
          <p class="hebrew">מעולם לא ראינו אדם כמוהו בחכמה ובקדושה</p>
          <p>"We have never seen a person like him in wisdom and holiness."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="praise-item">
          <p class="hebrew">הוא היה מלא רחמים וחסד לכל באי עולם</p>
          <p>"He was full of mercy and kindness to all the world."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="praise-item">
          <p class="hebrew">בכל דבריו היה מלא אמונה ובטחון בהשם</p>
          <p>"In all his words he was filled with faith and trust in Hashem."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="navigation">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>More Teachings</h2>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/teachings/sichos" class="nav-link">← Sichos HaRan</a>
        <a href="/teachings/likutay-eitzos" class="nav-link">Likutay Eitzos →</a>
        <a href="/teachings/sefer-hamidos" class="nav-link">Sefer HaMidos →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #975a16 0%, #d69e2e 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-hebrew);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid white;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .intro {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #fffaf0;
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
  }

  .topics {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .topics h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .topics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .topic-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    border-left: 4px solid #d69e2e;
  }

  .topic-card h3 {
    color: #975a16;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .topic-card p {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .quote {
    background: #975a16;
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quote blockquote {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote .hebrew {
    font-family: var(--font-hebrew);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .quote p {
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .featured-praises {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #fffaf0;
  }

  .featured-praises h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .praise-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .praise-item {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .praise-item .hebrew {
    font-family: var(--font-hebrew);
    color: #975a16;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .praise-item p:last-child {
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .navigation {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #fffaf0;
  }

  .navigation h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .nav-link {
    color: #975a16;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
